sentences: Chris Speed (born February 12, 1967) is an American saxophonist, clarinetist, and composer.

The co-led quartet Pachora was influenced by Balkan and Middle Eastern rhythms and said to be "immersed in Eastern European and Moroccan music", performing originals and Greek, Bulgarian and Turkish works.
